    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You raise some water into the air and turn it into countless needles to attack the target. The technique creates one needle, which is used to make a ranged attack at your highest attack bonus. If it hits, it deals 1d4 water damage. These attacks have Kawarimi Defense 1.<br><br>If you are (partially) submerged in water, you can increase the Perform Requirements by 5 to perform the technique without Half Seals.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to create an additional needle (up to 1 per level total), for which you may choose a new target. Creatures can be targeted by more than one needle.</p>\n\n",
